	accept nil as argument.

1999-10-17  Hiroshi IGARASHI  <igarashi@ueda.info.waseda.ac.jp>

	* src/rbgdk.c (make_gdkwindow, make_gdkpixmap, make_gdkbitmap):
	return Qnil for NULL.

